goals.active: Humble Nollarr and take his helm.
goals.complete: For Knut's special challenge, I chose Nollarr and his followers, Sons of Svanir who have been a problem near Svanir's Dome. The Sons fought will all their might, but I bested them and took Nollarr's prized helm for proof. I can only advance to the semifinals if I bring in the helm before my opponent arrives.
